## Özet - Workflows

1. **ci.yml** - Her push/PR'da build & test
2. **cd-docker.yml** - Main'e push'ta Docker build & push
3. **cd-k8s.yml** - Tag push veya manual deploy to K8s
4. **release.yml** - Tag push'ta GitHub release oluştur
5. **nightly.yml** - Her gece integration & performance test
6. **pr-checks.yml** - PR açıldığında code quality & security check

**CI/CD Flow:**
```
Developer Push → CI (Build/Test) → PR Checks → Merge to Main 
  → CD Docker (Build Images) → CD K8s (Deploy) → Release